  ";; Edit the command line for creating the tags file
;;
;; Syntax:
;;
;; - One command line argument in one line
;; - Lines start with ;; are ignored
;; - Use %TAGSFILE% to refer to the tags file
;; - \"%\" (other than those in %TAGSFILE%) and \"\\\" need escaping
